text: Volodymyr Shamenko (born 8 August 1972) is a Ukrainian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1996 Summer Olympics, winning a bronze medal in the men's artistic team all-around event. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Ukraine Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Medalists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic medalists in gymnastics Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Ukraine Category:People from Taraz
title: Volodymyr Shamenko
